schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2760147005/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2760147005","tinyui":"/x/PYCEp","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2760147005","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2760147005/Iniciativas+en+Curso","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2760147005"}},{"id":"3022520346","type":"page","ari":"ari:cloud:confluence:4e3a1a04-13f1-4674-95f6-44812aec1da3:page/3022520346","base64EncodedAri":"YXJpOmNsb3VkOmNvbmZsdWVuY2U6NGUzYTFhMDQtMTNmMS00Njc0LTk1ZjYtNDQ4MTJhZWMxZGEzOmNvbnRlbnQvMzAyMjUyMDM0Ng==","status":"current","title":"BAU","macroRenderedOutput":{},"extensions":{"position":868},"_expandable":{"container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","metadata":"","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/3022520346/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/3022520346/history","body":"","version":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/3022520346/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/3022520346/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/3022520346","tinyui":"/x/GgAot","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=3022520346","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/3022520346/BAU","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/3022520346"}}],"macroRenderedOutput":{},"body":{"storage":{"value":"<ac:structured-macro ac:name=\"info\" ac:schema-version=\"1\" ac:macro-id=\"92c06078-fd74-4dad-82c4-17a7aa8be336\"><ac:rich-text-body><p>Este documento representa el tasking y estimaci&oacute;n para <em>[doc de requerimientos de la iniciativa]. </em></p></ac:rich-text-body></ac:structured-macro><table data-table-width=\"760\" data-layout=\"default\" ac:local-id=\"d127e8c3-3fed-4af2-bc1b-c09b7117def2\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 395.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 111.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 253.0px;\" /></colgroup><tbody><tr><th><p><strong>Tarea</strong></p></th><th><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Estimaci&oacute;n (hs)</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Servicio / Portal</strong></p></th></tr><tr><td><p>Agregar el QR-WD como source v&aacute;lido en la generaci&oacute;n del QR</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">4</p></td><td><p>external-commerce-services</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Agregar en el modelo de payment hook el QR-WD como source valido</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">4</p></td><td><p>selling-service</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Implementar comunicaci&oacute;n con RPG para la consulta de comisi&oacute;n.</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">16</p></td><td><p>billing-proxy</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Agregar en el endpoint de decode, la comunicaci&oacute;n con el RPG para la consulta de la comisi&oacute;n seg&uacute;n la entidad.</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">6</p></td><td><p>billing-proxy</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Modificar respuesta de la decodificaci&oacute;n para devolver como datos opcionales los montos desglosados de extracci&oacute;n y comisi&oacute;n.</p><p>El campo &ldquo;amount&ldquo; debe tener el monto de extracci&oacute;n + comisi&oacute;n si el usuario es quien paga la comisi&oacute;n, sino solo el monto de la extracci&oacute;n.</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">6</p></td><td><p>billing-proxy</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Agregar en el endpoint de confirmaci&oacute;n, la comunicaci&oacute;n con el RPG para la consulta de la comisi&oacute;n seg&uacute;n la entidad. Enviar el monto de la comisi&oacute;n a selling-service.</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">8</p></td><td><p>billing-proxy</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Modificar endpoint de confirmaci&oacute;n para recibir el monto de la comisi&oacute;n.</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">6</p></td><td><p>selling-service</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Agregar validaci&oacute;n de que el medio de pago sea d&eacute;bito o d&eacute;bito en cuenta (solo para los QRs de extracci&oacute;n) sino debe fallar.</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">4</p></td><td><p>selling-service </p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Al momento de la validaci&oacute;n del medio de pago, si el medio de pago no es v&aacute;lido, notificar al comercio igualmente que el pago no se pudo realizar por esos motivos, y devolver respuesta acorde a la entidad.</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">16</p></td><td><p>selling-service</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Agregar en el llamado al JPOS el monto de la comisi&oacute;n.</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">6</p></td><td><p>selling-service</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Agregar el QR-source en la respuesta de la confirmaci&oacute;n.</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">4</p></td><td><p>selling-service</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Agregar el tipo de QR en la respuesta de la confirmaci&oacute;n de un QR.</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">4</p></td><td><p>billing-proxy</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Modificar el callback del POS para agregar los campos nuevos de QR-WD. Enviar 0 en esos campos si es un QR-BC o QR-Change.</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">12</p></td><td><p>selling-service</p></td></tr><tr><td><p /></td><td><p /></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p><strong>Total Desarrollo</strong></p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">96</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p /></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p><strong>Total Gesti&oacute;n 15% (para facturaci&oacute;n, no afecta el desarrollo)</strong></p><p><em>Incluye reuniones de estimaci&oacute;n, planificaci&oacute;n, t&eacute;cnicas y de seguimiento.</em></p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">14</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p /></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p><strong>Total Desarrollo + Gesti&oacute;n</strong></p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">110</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p /></td></tr></tbody></table><ac:adf-extension><ac:adf-node type=\"panel\"><ac:adf-attribute key=\"panel-type\">note</ac:adf-attribute><ac:adf-content><p>Preguntas</p></ac:adf-content></ac:adf-node><ac:adf-fallback><div class=\"panel conf-macro output-block\" style=\"background-color: rgb(234,230,255);border-color: rgb(153,141,217);border-width: 1.0px;\"><div class=\"panelContent\" style=\"background-color: rgb(234,230,255);\">\n<p>Preguntas</p>\n</div></div></ac:adf-fallback></ac:adf-extension><table data-table-width=\"760\" data-layout=\"default\" ac:local-id=\"df39bc32-2722-40c6-b433-4529f0480f16\"><tbody><tr><td><p>Como quieren manejar el permiso para que el comercio cree QRs de vuelto. Hoy en d&iacute;a no tenemos esta validaci&oacute;n para el QR de cambio.</p></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td><p>Para el caso de QR_Change es configurable que entidades soportan esas confirmaciones. Queremos lo mismo para QR vuelto?</p></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td><p>Como hacemos para saber si el medio de pago es d&eacute;bito o d&eacute;bito en cuenta? Alcanza con que el account type sea debit? </p></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td><p>El jpos que se va a usar va a ser el mismo que se usa para el qr_change y qr_bc?</p></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td><p>Queremos configurar un m&aacute;ximo para los retiros? </p></td><td><p /></td></tr></tbody></table>","representation":"storage","embeddedContent":[],"_expandable":{"content":"/rest/api/content/3242623368"}},"_expandable":{"editor":"","atlas_doc_format":"","view":"","export_view":"","styled_view":"","dynamic":"","editor2":"","anonymous_export_view":""}},"extensions":{"position":2530},"_expandable":{"childTypes":"","container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","schedulePublishInfo":"","metadata":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/3242623368/child","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/3242623368/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/3242623368/history","draftVersion":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/3242623368/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN"},"_links":{"editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=3242623368","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/3242623368/Extracciones+en+POS+con+QR+-+Tasking+y+Estimaci+n","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/3242623368","context":"/wiki","self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/3242623368","tinyui":"/x/iIFGwQ","collection":"/rest/api/content","base":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki"}}